Package team1351.purepursuit

Class TrajectoryPoint

  • java.lang.Object
    • TrajectoryPoint
  • public class TrajectoryPoint
extends java.lang.Object
    The master object for any point on the path. The point contains an x and y coordinate, a position along the path, a velocity value at this point, and a curvature of the point.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Owen Leather
